585
00:33:35,540 --> 00:33:35,980
Chief Lin.

586
00:33:36,620 --> 00:33:37,660
Yunhui?

587
00:33:38,780 --> 00:33:39,380
Go then.

588
00:34:09,900 --> 00:34:10,620
Chen Yu.

589
00:34:12,660 --> 00:34:13,620
What are you doing? Let's go.

590
00:34:13,660 --> 00:34:14,220
Coming.

591
00:34:15,700 --> 00:34:16,700
This time, it'll be difficult

592
00:34:16,740 --> 00:34:17,940
