593
00:34:18,140 --> 00:34:19,500
Mind your own business.

594
00:34:20,860 --> 00:34:22,020
Who's Feng exactly?

595
00:34:24,100 --> 00:34:25,300
I said that I have never met him.

596
00:34:28,460 --> 00:34:29,620
Your pharmacy is targeted now.

597
00:34:29,940 --> 00:34:30,820
He robbed you just now,

598
00:34:31,140 --> 00:34:32,100
and he might rob you again.

599
00:34:32,500 --> 00:34:33,340
Why don't you just put the rest of stock

600
00:34:33,340 --> 00:34:34,060
at my place?

601
00:34:34,220 --> 00:34:34,980
First, it's safe.

602
00:34:35,220 --> 00:34:36,020
What's more, I can sell them for you.

603
00:34:36,420 --> 00:34:36,980
This way, I can make up

604
00:34:36,980 --> 00:34:37,980
for the money I owe you.

605
00:34:40,620 --> 00:34:42,860
[L]

606
00:34:53,180 --> 00:34:53,700
Hello.

607
00:34:54,340 --> 00:34:55,180
Are you at the pharmacy?

608
00:34:56,540 --> 00:34:57,540
Someone reported you to the police.

609
00:34:57,940 --> 00:34:58,820
The police will be there soon.

610
00:35:05,660 --> 00:35:06,460
What's wrong?

611
00:35:07,300 --> 00:35:09,540
I-I'm reported.

612
00:35:10,660 --> 00:35:12,180
It must be that brat just now.

613
00:35:18,460 --> 00:35:19,020
Peng.

614
00:35:19,540 --> 00:35:20,540
Just leave them to me.

615
00:35:20,700 --> 00:35:21,500
It's safe indeed.

616
00:35:22,540 --> 00:35:23,860
You have to return the money.

617
00:35:23,980 --> 00:35:24,780
Don't worry.

618
00:35:25,420 --> 00:35:26,220
I'll go then.

619
00:36:21,180 --> 00:36:21,820
Hello.

620
00:36:22,820 --> 00:36:24,020
We are from the Counter Narcotics Unit

621
00:36:24,060 --> 00:36:25,100
of Yunhe Public Security Bureau.

622
00:36:25,380 --> 00:36:27,100
We'll investigate your place according to the law.

623
00:36:27,540 --> 00:36:28,340
Please cooperate.

624
00:36:28,740 --> 00:36:29,580
Officer.

625
00:36:30,020 --> 00:36:30,940
What's going on?

626
00:36:33,220 --> 00:36:34,140
Are there narcotics?

627
00:36:35,180 --> 00:36:36,740
There must be a misunderstanding.

628
00:36:37,340 --> 00:36:38,460
I run this place lawfully.

629
00:36:38,500 --> 00:36:39,580
How would it be involved in narcotics?

630
00:37:17,380 --> 00:37:18,140
Captain Liu.

631
00:37:26,940 --> 00:37:27,860
Where's its packaging?

632
00:37:29,580 --> 00:37:30,940
It was like this when purchased.

633
00:37:31,620 --> 00:37:33,380
It was like this when purchased?

634
00:37:34,540 --> 00:37:35,940
It's the normal medicine for the cold.

635
00:37:35,940 --> 00:37:36,940
I can explain.

636
00:37:38,180 --> 00:37:40,420
OK, explain to us at our unit.

637
00:37:40,620 --> 00:37:40,900
Take him.

638
00:37:40,900 --> 00:37:42,220
It's a misunderstanding, officer.

639
00:37:42,620 --> 00:37:43,140
Anran.

640
00:37:43,420 --> 00:37:44,500
Take it back for an assay.

641
00:37:44,580 --> 00:37:44,820
Roger that.

642
00:37:44,820 --> 00:37:45,980
Qiang, we'll leave first.

643
00:37:46,060 --> 00:37:46,940
Continue investigating.

644
00:37:51,220 --> 00:37:52,060
So you are finally

645
00:37:52,060 --> 00:37:52,860
calling me.

646
00:37:52,900 --> 00:37:53,940
Something is wrong, Xian.

647
00:37:54,940 --> 00:37:56,380
Ba's pharmacy got reported to the police.

648
00:37:56,740 --> 00:37:57,420
What did you say?

649
00:37:57,660 --> 00:37:58,820
The drug is robbed.

650
00:37:59,540 --> 00:38:00,940
Ba was captured by police.

651
00:38:01,660 --> 00:38:02,460
Who did that?

652
00:38:03,540 --> 00:38:04,620
Someone called Feng.

653
00:38:07,060 --> 00:38:08,260
He said he knew you.

654
00:38:08,860 --> 00:38:11,700
I think it's okay if Ba is captured.

655
00:38:12,660 --> 00:38:13,420
You still have me.

656
00:38:14,260 --> 00:38:16,980
You can give me the rest of the stock

657
00:38:17,980 --> 00:38:18,380
and I can

658
00:38:18,380 --> 00:38:19,660
return the money I owe you.

659
00:38:20,580 --> 00:38:22,020
I will earn you a great fortune.

660
00:38:22,940 --> 00:38:23,900
You broke the rule.

661
00:38:24,380 --> 00:38:25,740
I'll give you three days.

662
00:38:26,060 --> 00:38:27,100
Within three days,

663
00:38:27,340 --> 00:38:28,380
if you can't return the money,

664
00:38:28,780 --> 00:38:31,180
you know what you'll face.

665
00:38:37,020 --> 00:38:37,900
You won't give it to me? Fine.

666
00:38:38,700 --> 00:38:40,020
Who do you think you are?

667
00:38:46,660 --> 00:38:47,340
Your name?

668
00:38:49,300 --> 00:38:49,660
Ba Peng.

669
00:38:49,660 --> 00:38:50,140
Ba is for the bus.

670
00:38:50,180 --> 00:38:50,980
Peng is for the roc.

671
00:38:51,020 --> 00:38:52,140
My friends call me Ba.

672
00:38:52,740 --> 00:38:53,300
Your age?

673
00:38:54,220 --> 00:38:54,940
Thirty-three.

674
00:38:56,140 --> 00:38:56,780
Your occupation?

675
00:38:57,260 --> 00:38:58,380
I run a little pharmacy.

676
00:38:58,420 --> 00:38:59,500
The one you investigated,

677
00:38:59,500 --> 00:39:00,420
Yunhui Pharmacy.

678
00:39:01,140 --> 00:39:03,020
You were in jail for three years
because of taking and dealing narcotics

679
00:39:03,060 --> 00:39:04,580
and were released in January last year.

680
00:39:08,900 --> 00:39:10,100
Do you have anything to tell us?

681
00:39:10,500 --> 00:39:11,300
I've turned over a new leaf.

682
00:39:11,300 --> 00:39:12,780
I'm now a proper merchant.

683
00:39:14,220 --> 00:39:15,660
Then tell us about the item

684
00:39:15,660 --> 00:39:16,820
we found in your place.

685
00:39:17,500 --> 00:39:18,180
The capsules are just

686
00:39:18,180 --> 00:39:19,060
Paracetamol Caffein Atificial Cow-bezoar
and chlorphenamine Maleate capsules.

687
00:39:19,100 --> 00:39:20,140
They are used to treat normal colds

688
00:39:20,180 --> 00:39:21,420
and those symptoms caused by flu,

689
00:39:21,460 --> 00:39:22,580
namely fever, headache, rhinobyon...

690
00:39:22,580 --> 00:39:23,500
Don't recite those to me.

691
00:39:24,580 --> 00:39:25,380
Where is the packaging?

692
00:39:36,060 --> 00:39:36,900
I threw it away.

693
00:39:38,420 --> 00:39:39,460
It is not the same

694
00:39:39,500 --> 00:39:40,500
as you mentioned at the pharmacy.

695
00:39:44,140 --> 00:39:45,420
Then I must get it wrong.

696
00:39:45,900 --> 00:39:47,020
It was like this when purchased.

697
00:39:54,020 --> 00:39:55,540
No medicine can be sold

698
00:39:55,580 --> 00:39:56,620
to a pharmacy without packaging.

699
00:39:57,460 --> 00:39:58,700
Unless it's not medicine.

700
00:40:04,700 --> 00:40:06,580
Say it! What's it?

701
00:40:10,380 --> 00:40:11,020
Officers.

702
00:40:11,100 --> 00:40:11,940
I'll say it.

703
00:40:12,700 --> 00:40:14,380
Those were bought from other counties.

704
00:40:15,220 --> 00:40:17,340
I admit it is fake medicine.

705
00:40:18,020 --> 00:40:19,300
The true ones cost four yuan each pack.

706
00:40:19,340 --> 00:40:20,420
I can only earn less than one yuan with that.

707
00:40:20,460 --> 00:40:21,740
But the fakes can earn me over one yuan each.

708
00:40:22,060 --> 00:40:23,340
So I bought three packs of them.

709
00:40:37,780 --> 00:40:38,540
Do you know him?

710
00:40:43,980 --> 00:40:44,860
What do you mean?

711
00:40:46,500 --> 00:40:47,060
Nothing.

712
00:40:47,580 --> 00:40:48,220
I'm just asking.

713
00:40:52,140 --> 00:40:52,980
What about the empty one?

714
00:40:53,180 --> 00:40:54,180
Where's its content?

715
00:40:55,060 --> 00:40:55,860
I took them.

716
00:40:56,420 --> 00:40:57,420
You took them?

717
00:40:58,460 --> 00:41:00,140
Aren't you afraid of the poison?

718
00:41:01,020 --> 00:41:02,340
I caught a cold some time ago,

719
00:41:02,340 --> 00:41:03,780
so I tried them myself.

720
00:41:04,460 --> 00:41:06,220
I thought I could purchase more of them
if it was effective.

721
00:41:06,620 --> 00:41:07,060
But it turned out

722
00:41:07,060 --> 00:41:07,940
it was useless.

723
00:41:07,980 --> 00:41:09,100
So I threw them away without finishing them.

724
00:41:10,980 --> 00:41:12,500
Let's drop the fact
whether it's medicine for a cold inside.

725
00:41:12,540 --> 00:41:13,260
I'm telling you.

726
00:41:13,620 --> 00:41:15,740
It's illegal to sell fake medicine.

727
00:41:15,780 --> 00:41:16,860
You will be sentenced.

728
00:41:16,860 --> 00:41:17,700
Do you know that?

729
00:41:17,900 --> 00:41:18,860
I didn't sell them. I didn't.

730
00:41:19,420 --> 00:41:20,620
I gave them all to you.

731
00:41:25,900 --> 00:41:27,300
If there's no problem, just let him go.

732
00:41:44,140 --> 00:41:44,940
What would you like to have?

733
00:41:45,740 --> 00:41:47,020
Go to the old warehouse

734
00:41:47,220 --> 00:41:48,340
and fake a scene.

735
00:41:48,900 --> 00:41:50,100
Report to the police

736
00:41:50,420 --> 00:41:52,060
that Hu Qingshan was killed by him.

737
00:41:52,820 --> 00:41:53,700
By him?

